# Components & Hooks

## Components (`app/components/`)

- Default export per file; `'use client'` when using hooks or events.
- Guide UI split: `OnboardingGuide` → `GuideEngineer` + `GuideSpeechBubble` (avoid deep nested `<div>` blocks that are easy to corrupt).
- Auth wrapper: `AuthShell`; home flow: `HomeEntry`.

## Hooks (`app/hooks/`)

- Shared client hooks only (e.g. `useTypewriter.ts`).
- Do not import server-only modules into hooks.

## JSX safety

- Use `<div>`, `<section>`, `<figure>` — never `motion.div` (not installed).
- Prefer small subcomponents over 100+ line JSX trees.
